tags.name: LT 28 Traffic Cameras/LT-56 Traffic Camera LHS panel

testSteps.description: Given I am at the LiveTraffic Website
When I click on the menu button
And I click "Traffic Cameras" button from the menu list

Then I should see list of Camera regions from All Cameras tab
| Camera_Region |
| Inner Sydney |
| Sydney North |
| Sydney West |
| Sydney South |
| Regional North |
| Regional South |
| All Regional |
| All NSW |
| All Sydney |
When I click "Sydney South" button from All Cameras List
Then I should Camera Region name "Sydney South" on page

Then I should see list of below cameras from "Sydney South" region
| Camera_Locations |
| 5 Ways (Miranda) |
| Hume Highway (Bankstown) |
| Hume Motorway (Campbelltown) |
| Hume Highway (Cumberland Highway, Liverpool) |
| Hume Motorway (St Andrews) |
| Hume Highway (Villawood) |
| M5 / M7 |
| M5 (Liverpool) |
| M5 (Milperra) |
| Audley Road (Audley Weir) |
| Princes Highway (Heathcote) |
| M5 (Padstow) |
| Princes Highway (Sutherland) |
| Narellan Road (Campbelltown) |
| New Illawarra Road (Bangor Bypass) |
| Hume Highway (Elizabeth Drive, Liverpool) |
When I click back arrow button

Then I should see list of Camera regions from All Cameras tab
| Camera_Region |
| Inner Sydney |
| Sydney North |
| Sydney West |
| Sydney South |
